{"id": 2232, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些对女孩的教育必不可少？", "description": "可别只知道说“找工作轻松最重要”了。", "record_count": 6411, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803181743175GDHNc70VCfsTUrh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 271360, "content": "女孩一定要活的精致 美是爽给自己看的 不是别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249504}, {"id": 271616, "content": "女孩子应该要少被人操，然后多学跆拳道，结果你走到哪个国家都是安全的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227674}, {"id": 271361, "content": "不要满脑子都是钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290265}, {"id": 271617, "content": "多读书好好学习，自己强大是最重要的，别听什么女孩子太强势以后嫁不出去，你的价值不在于嫁人。\n少看些三观有问题的东西，微博还有小说电视剧里面的，看看就好，别作天作地的然后还怨男生不够爱你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291080}, {"id": 271362, "content": "独立。适当撒娇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275936}, {"id": 271365, "content": "没有确定关系之前不要整天找男的帮忙，做一些超出合理范围的事，找备胎的行为真的很讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939417}, {"id": 271621, "content": "能为自己决定生活，而不是靠人家的想法活着，做最好的自己，而不是人家眼里最美的你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291079}, {"id": 271366, "content": "仪表仪容举止言谈教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682613}, {"id": 271367, "content": "强大自己 不依赖他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290284}, {"id": 271623, "content": "自尊自爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279383}, {"id": 271368, "content": "如今的社会对女性有歧视，这需要得到改变。这个改变应该从女孩自己开始。女性应该明白：自己的生命，自己的生活需要靠自己，而不是男性。同时，要了解并争取女性应有的权利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68155}, {"id": 273672, "content": "爱情和婚姻不是你的头等大事，只是一部分而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 271369, "content": "保持独立思考。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231045}, {"id": 271370, "content": "你首先是你个人，接下来才是个女人，当然，你也可以选择不当女人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268977}, {"id": 271626, "content": "网络的言情小说别看太多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278049}, {"id": 271371, "content": "少说蠢话，保持自己的看法", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287748}, {"id": 271627, "content": "自尊自爱自强", "image": "img/option/option/20180320161953NCvVqtm9Q5zY0D1P", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290977}, {"id": 274443, "content": "多謝各位。另外，\"直男\"不是貶義詞吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089950}, {"id": 274955, "content": "性教育，独立思考，自尊并尊重他人，运动或健身，艺术教育，九年义务教育…太多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 271372, "content": "我想要说的是其他人的评论太好了，如果有个收藏功能就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284878}, {"id": 271373, "content": "喜欢什么就努力去争取", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274553}, {"id": 271374, "content": "淡定", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232159}, {"id": 272398, "content": "学会自居，还有就是多读古诗宋词", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141832}, {"id": 271375, "content": "自信  善良", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283381}, {"id": 271887, "content": "如何看待自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091485}, {"id": 271376, "content": "不强调性别特征的教育。请出题的编辑好好反思一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163303}, {"id": 271377, "content": "别觉得自己是女王 全世界都要给你让道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 271889, "content": "在一味强调自己权利的时候 也要尊重别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286590}, {"id": 271378, "content": "拜金，什么都和人家比。没有自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 271379, "content": "女孩一点也不比男孩差，结婚生子应该是出于个人期盼，绝不是每个女孩子的使命和任务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226297}, {"id": 271891, "content": "自爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292005}, {"id": 271380, "content": "可能我比较肤浅 我觉得女孩子富养真的很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290185}, {"id": 271636, "content": "基本可以明显看出是男的还是女的写的。男的在提要求女的在提建议。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856027}, {"id": 271892, "content": "自爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292005}, {"id": 271381, "content": "自尊，自爱，自信，自强", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267449}, {"id": 271893, "content": "自爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292005}, {"id": 271383, "content": "会阅读，写作的女生真的真的不多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287004}, {"id": 271384, "content": "少看迷蒙?‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290330}, {"id": 271640, "content": "不被传统观念所束缚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291086}, {"id": 271385, "content": "少看咪蒙", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290330}, {"id": 272923, "content": "不要为了所谓的“维持”这个家而忍受另一半的各种暴力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632130}, {"id": 271388, "content": "在别人说，“女孩子应该怎样怎样”的时候清楚的明白，女孩并不是应该怎样怎样。用实力反击。告诉他们，女孩子也可以这样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217164}, {"id": 271389, "content": "女孩子一生要有50%的知识傍身，因为无论遇到什么最终都需要自己有一技在身；需要有45%的爱，大爱小爱让你体会美妙；还需要5%的识大体和自信！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290307}, {"id": 271390, "content": "要有自己愿意为之付出时间的爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290340}, {"id": 271391, "content": "男性生理课\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290347}, {"id": 271136, "content": "男的不懂化妆品什么的就说别人是直男，你是不是脑子有坑，一个大男人没事去研究化妆品干嘛，那你女的不会打球或者打机是不是钢铁直女", "image": null, "praise_count": 921, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227649}, {"id": 271392, "content": "不好意思，有气质就可以为所欲为", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166392}, {"id": 271137, "content": "多读书，阅读太重要了", "image": null, "praise_count": 694, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599749}, {"id": 271393, "content": "洁身自好，勿爱慕虚荣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306892}, {"id": 274977, "content": "自我意识的觉醒：外在美貌的探索与挖掘，内心不取悦任何人的建设与坚定", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288780}]}